snippet.title: Ha_Bits: Prologue
snippet.description:
Ha_Bits is an Adventure and platformer game for windows and Mac OS with a neo-noir cyberpunk setting.

We would love for you to be part of this project on Patreon!
https://www.patreon.com/Ha_Bits

Find us on Steam! and be aware of Ha_Bits: Prologue launch on August 13th, 2021.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1696020/Ha_Bits_Prologue/

Enjoy our Ha_Bits discord channel https://discord.gg/Zj34e3nS 

Visit us on http://www.darkquixotestudio.com
Follow us on twitter https://twitter.com/quixote_dark
Any questions about our projects? you can send us an e-mail to darkquixotestudio@gmail.com

#Cyberpunk #indiegames
